<section id="overview" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="overview">Overview</h2>
<p>Electrifying energy, and decarbonizing electricity. Power system is at the center of global energy transtion. This research theme explores the pathways and their environmental, climate, human health, and socio-economic implications.</p>
</section>
