<item>
  <title>China Carbon Neutrality Initiative</title>
  <link>http://deeppolicylab.github.io/research/china-carbon-neutrality-initiative/</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 




<p><img src="http://deeppolicylab.github.io/research/china-carbon-neutrality-initiative/featured.png" class="img-fluid"></p>
<section id="overview" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="overview">Overview</h2>
<p>China is the world’s largest emitter of greenhouse gases. It has set a target to achieve carbon peak by 2030 and carbon neutrality by 2060. This initiative aims to facilitate the transition to a low-carbon economy in China to achieve the national carbon peak and carbon neutrality targets.</p>
</section>
<section id="featured-publications" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="featured-publications">Featured publications</h2>
<div id="listing-china-carbon-papers" class="quarto-listing quarto-listing-container-grid">
<div class="list grid quarto-listing-cols-2">
<div class="g-col-1" data-index="0" data-listing-date-sort="1646110800000">
<a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/s43017-021-00244-x" class="quarto-grid-link">
<div class="quarto-grid-item card h-100 card-left">
<p class="card-img-top">
<img loading="lazy" src="http://deeppolicylab.github.io/files/images/journal/nature-reviews-earth.jpg" class="thumbnail-image card-img" style="height: 200px;">
</p>
<div class="card-body post-contents">
<h5 class="no-anchor card-title listing-title">
Challenges and opportunities for carbon neutrality in China
</h5>
<div class="card-subtitle listing-subtitle">
<em>Nature Reviews Earth &amp; Environment</em>
</div>
<div class="card-text listing-description">
In this Perspective, we summarize the key features of China’s CO2 emissions, its reduction processes and successes in meeting climate targets.
</div>
<div class="card-attribution card-text-small end">
<div class="listing-date">
Mar 1, 2022
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</a>
</div>
<div class="g-col-1" data-index="1" data-listing-date-sort="1597982400000">
<a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.oneear.2020.07.012" class="quarto-grid-link">
<div class="quarto-grid-item card h-100 card-left">
<p class="card-img-top">
<img loading="lazy" src="http://deeppolicylab.github.io/files/images/journal/one-earth-logo.jpg" class="thumbnail-image card-img" style="height: 200px;">
</p>
<div class="card-body post-contents">
<h5 class="no-anchor card-title listing-title">
Enabling a Rapid and Just Transition away from Coal in China
</h5>
<div class="card-subtitle listing-subtitle">
<em>One Earth</em>
</div>
<div class="card-text listing-description">
Aggressive coal-transition pathway is needed to achieve carbon nutrality goal while achieving water saving, avoiding premature death.
</div>
<div class="card-attribution card-text-small end">
<div class="listing-date">
Aug 21, 2020
</div>
</div>
</div>
